Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的阳光就快来临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照进这间充满烟蒂\N杂乱无章的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 圣母玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对温柔感到饥渴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么孤单的夜晚\N总是如此漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔裤下的膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的梦想打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着衬衫的胸部太过耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失恋?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,狠狠的被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了你还这么开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其闷在心里感到烦闷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说出来,然后把它忘了\N这样比较健康
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沮丧消沈跟我的个性不合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,尽情地喝\N然后忘得一干二净最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道我也有错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是怎么可以突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沮丧消沈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪头,阪本\N是我…是我啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#69水中大混战!\N五代身上可疑的吻痕!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天真的到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶\N能不能麻烦您帮我看家一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傍晚就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,隔壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N还让你特地送我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打完网球流了一身汗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯冰凉的啤酒最棒了\N要不要进来坐一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了,我到这里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗,反正我是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啤酒,喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-音无小姐\N-什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,明天你有空吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是某家饭店的会员\N那里有游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的话\N我想邀你一起去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,虽然打网球也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,夏天最棒的还是在艳阳下\N在游泳池尽情游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到你了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有,我没这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天闲得发慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他放着我这个千里迢迢\N跑来看他的老人家不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都往外面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近好像忙着找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我们代替五代\N带奶奶去游泳池玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好?音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样说定罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会当你们的电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,期待明天的游泳罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔去游泳也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?很适合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要去饭店的游泳池游泳\N所以才买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭店的游泳池?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,三鹰教练邀请我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会管理员也要去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心的话,你要不要也一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在忙着找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,我先去洗个澡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了,昨天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你今天也要去找工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到一辈子的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我得学好自己打领带才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天也会很热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然会在这种地方打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,不好意思\N这家饭店的游泳池很贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的事情就别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰教练是有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思\N连我们都一起被你请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\N我早就料到你们会跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才多三个人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,肚量很大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都来了\N五代也一起来的话才更有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明今天一天没去找工作\N又没什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛,反正一定找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能不能顺利毕业还是个问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算毕业也会变成无业游民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代好像摆脱不了\N落榜的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像鱼板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N大家拼命在讲我的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,怎么这么巧\N大家都跑来我打工的饭店游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N你一个人在这里嘀咕什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会很不妙\N因为我跟他们说我去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛撒这种谎啊,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗?音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?没有,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我们去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以说谎,不可以说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道你是失恋\N还是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是把我这个月房租都喝掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里的哪一位啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我介绍打工给你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单只是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…还留下了这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了?这不是吻痕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我当成女的\N紧紧抱着我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我装糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想吐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作不认识他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N那群人到哪里都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混帐,趁我不在\N就一直黏着管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,五代也真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年我是等到了秋天\N才开始找工作的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…居然做出像情侣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面说可以轮流午休了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了,绝对饶不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务生在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去买个啤酒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候\N五代在的话就很方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,各位都在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你正忙着找工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为离下午的面试\N还有一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然付得起游泳池的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点钱我也有好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也过来这里喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便买点啤酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池不是饮酒作乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我再去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你脖子怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被虫咬到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是吻痕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?过来让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,奶奶也一起来游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,您游得好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我年轻的时候\N可是被称为''海滨女王''呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,我们来比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦,跟个白痴似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,她真的游得好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鱿鱼干\N本来就是海里的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌\N你怎么这样说你奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,她真的很像鱿鱼干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷做体操
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你的OK绷呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?掉到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不太像被虫咬的伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶…奶奶,不要吓我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也终于变成男人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我装糊涂\N这是什么,这明明就是吻痕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪你最近都很晚才回来\N原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是谁?是小津江?\N还是那个高中女生?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来\N前天晚上你没有回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明有打电话给你啊\N说我要在阪本家过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的,这个也是阪本…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里打工,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,你是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间你在干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道看不出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不过五代我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在失恋很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是想让我更伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的面子怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说出去\N这样彼此都会没面子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务生,去拿红豆饭来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝我孙子变成男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾的,这里没有红豆饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?管理员呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她早就上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管她是小津江还是谁都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,究竟是谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气,只要能让你高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是阪本吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这付打扮?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是服务生,在这里打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好\N服务生,快拿啤酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿多一点来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说前天五代在你家过夜啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?五代吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?这就奇怪了\N前天晚上没人来我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟,你真的误会了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阪本睡昏了头…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,吻痕!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁亲的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了,是阪本他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是阪本说前天没有人住他家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好害羞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一两个吻痕,我经常有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是能光明正大说出来的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是被女生吻的\N我也想光明正大说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事的确没什么好炫耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的误会我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然要解释
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我居然把她抱在怀里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他抢先了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过一两个吻痕\N干嘛气成那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人的个性\N都很容易认真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作和管理员\N到底是什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这个问题问得太尖锐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从很久以前\N就想知道他们是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻痕跟齿痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个激情的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好猛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个吻痕是我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你们是那种关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多也该上来了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么事让你不高兴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,我只是想一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想拜托一之濑太太或朱美\N帮我拿大毛巾过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是行不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员还在游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的很危险喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,服务生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得那位服务生\N长得好像五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳后喝的酒特别好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,一之濑太太\N你有下去游泳吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于五代的吻痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这件事没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对被隐藏的事实没兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那个吻痕是阪本弄的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说下午有个面试吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,结果好像还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,以后还有很多机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年春天我一定会成为\N独当一面的社会人士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上楼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在游泳池,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛那么爱面子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流逝的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印刻在手臂上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉儿鸣叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么诗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,新干线停了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说线路发生了意外
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在恢复通车前\N好好喝一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:23:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“再见了,奶奶!\N上野车站陷入宴会混乱”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人坐在黎明的护栏上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在寻找遗落爱的地方
